#kt-note(id: "notes/notes/2026-02-25-panel-glue-ups.typ", title: "panel-glue-ups", tags: ("woodworking"), author: "", date: "2026-02-25", api => [
= Checks
  - Check square
  - Check alignment before glue-up
  - Slight bow towards edges good as it ensures even pressure

= Glue-up
  - Glue on both edges
  - Clamps on either side
  - Use clamps on joint edges to ensure alignement there
  - Use cauls (slightly curved to ensure even pressure) to ensure alignment along the edge
])
